data.description: Great opportunity! First time on the Market! One Owner! This beautiful Raised Ranch style home was built in 1988, is close to Route 302 and the Maine Turnpike, features 3 bedrooms, 2-3/4 bathrooms, 1616 Square Ft, and 11.64 private acres of land! This amazing home offers hardwood floors, laminate, tile (in kitchen, bathrooms, laundry room, and entryway) and carpeting in the bedrooms. This property also features a full finished basement with a woodstove, an attached 1 car garage, and a detached 1 car garage with a workshop and storage upstairs. The home also includes an inviting outdoor area, perfect for entertaining, with a fabulous brick outdoor fireplace, large back deck, cozy gazebo, with views of a nearby pond. Don't miss this opportunity to own this impressive property!!
